      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist's specification, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six utilizing individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing. The drivetrain features the sought-after Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox paired with a responsive M-Variable Differential Lock. Mechanical upkeep is evident, including preventative subframe reinforcement and a recent valve adjustment. The chassis retains its balance through well-sorted bushings and dampers, offering exceptional lateral grip and feedback. It presents in strong driver condition, ideal for those who value mechanical pedigree and analog performance.",
